I was trying to debug a separate issue earlier this week, but I added a print line to CommandScheduler.getInstance().onCommandInitialized(…) and it appears that whenever the code schedules a command it does it multiple times.

Screenshot 2025-03-26 at 12.43.18 PM520×790 7.15 KB

I am currently trying to fix overrun issues and I believe this could be part of the problem. Any ideas/insights are greatly appreciated!
